About Us
Crafted for Relaxation. Built to Impress.
At
Nicks Tiki Bars
, we bring tropical style and lasting craftsmanship together in every piece we make. What started as a passion for backyard upgrades has grown into a full collection of handcrafted Tiki bars designed to transform any space—indoors or out.
Whether you're looking for a cozy
U-Shape Classic
for your patio, a stylish
L-Shape Signature
for your basement, or a custom bar that doubles as a reception desk or cash wrap, we’ve got the shape and style to match your vision.
Every bar is built with:
Premium materials
Attention to detail
Customizable options
A touch of island flair
We believe a bar is more than just furniture—it’s a place to gather, relax, celebrate, and create memories. That’s why we focus on both design and durability, giving you something that looks amazing and lasts for years.
From backyards to businesses, Nicks Tiki Bars brings a vibe that fits wherever life happens.
